      "message": "it is generally safer to close a channel in the same piece of code which created it. It prevents situations where we close a closed channel. Given that you will end up expanding `go resultsForRequest()` into `go func() { ... }`, you recommend putting the defer there\n\nthen comments like L137-138 aren\u0027t needed\n\nsame below",
